'''Bargoon Tatooni''' was a privately owned trading post in [[Mos Eisley/Legends|Mos Eisley]] on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]. It was often the site of an annual [[Jawa/Legends|Jawa]] rendezvous and [[swap meet]], and it had the best prices on [[Starship/Legends|spacecraft]] parts and cookware. Bargoon Tatooni was eventually absorbed into the [[The galaxy/Legends|galaxy]]-wide [[Barguna Moocha]] chain.

